DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun morning of space exploration! We will be making a galaxy in a bottle\, have fun crafts\, space books\, and more! It’s going to be an out of this world experience! \nTickets needed for each child. Max of 2 caregivers are free! \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
