SUMMARY:Live Music with Mr. Ben – Tuesdays at the Hostel Cafe!
DESCRIPTION:Join us for live music with children’s performer Mr. Ben\, a fun show designed for kids (ages newborn through 5) —but enjoyable for adults too! This free\, family-friendly event (tips encouraged) is a relaxed space for families to sing\, move\, and socialize together.\n\nWe have indoor and outdoor seating\, scratch-made local dinners\, and 12 drinks on tap plus wine—something for everyone to enjoy while the kids play and sing along. Check out hostelcafepdx.com for more details! No rsvp needed.
